Bank Application tasks

a. accounts (savings/current)
1. create account.
2. deposit/withdraw money.
3. check balance.
4. view / edit account details.
5. give loan.
6. loan status.
7. account details.

b. admin
1. add / remove employee.
2. view details of all the accounts.
3. see all loan status.

c. employee
1. edit their profiles.
2. login/logout.


